1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,160
What did you just say?

2
00:00:02,640 --> 00:00:03,400
Tell me!

3
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:04,080
What?

4
00:00:04,440 --> 00:00:06,480
If I tell you,
can you promise me something?

5
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:10,080
That you'll protect
the young lady's happiness.

6
00:00:10,120 --> 00:00:11,600
Can you promise me that?

7
00:00:12,640 --> 00:00:13,480
I have something to say.

8
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:15,080
It's about what happened
in high school.

9
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:19,320
The truth is,
someone paid me...

10
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:20,440
...to pretend to be
her boyfriend.

11
00:00:24,080 --> 00:00:26,160
I don't know any of the details.

12
00:00:26,480 --> 00:00:27,800
Why would you do that?

13
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,440
Like I said, I don't know!

14
00:00:29,520 --> 00:00:30,720
If you're not going to be straight with me,

15
00:00:31,480 --> 00:00:33,120
you can forget about getting paid.

16
00:00:33,160 --> 00:00:34,160
No, no.
Hold on.

17
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,640
I honestly don't know anything else!

18
00:00:38,120 --> 00:00:38,680
But...

19
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:39,440
What?

20
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:42,080
But I do know
one crazy thing.

21
00:00:42,560 --> 00:00:43,120
What is it?

22
00:00:43,280 --> 00:00:44,960
Who that person really is.
